name: Fifth Generation Technologies India Private
overview:
Fifth Generation Technologies India Private Limited, an outsourced software product development company, develops and implements automation solutions and products for the manufacturing, advertising, finance, law enforcement, hospitality, and sports industries. Its products include Enterprise Maintenance Gateway (EMG), which provides real time integration between the manufacturing and enterprise operations; eZ Analytix, a plug and play reporting and visualization software that integrates to various applications or data sources; Adworks Pro, a business process management software that helps advertising, public relations, brand marketing, and design companies in the management and tracking of jobs within the firm; Enterprise Gateway Ontology Mapping Services, a module of EMG, which streamlines the passage of information and helps in generating third party actions in other systems; Law Office Assistant, which helps in managing the activities of a law firm; and Resort Xpert, an ERP for the resort reservation market, which integrates information from across the organization and produces operating documents. The company also offers robotic products to the pharmaceutical, automobile, electronic, food, and manufacturing and assembly industries, as well as to commercial laboratories. Fifth Generation Technologies India Private Limited has strategic tie-ups with JP Research Inc., Tenth Power Inc., Vector Solutions Inc, Automatika Ltd., EnteGreat Canada Inc., and IPath Technologies Private Limited.

The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Chennai, India. Fifth Generation Technologies India Private Limited operates as a subsidiary of 5th Generation Technologies, Inc.
